general.content:
A full Leather store demo with all what you need to build a custom theme with Momizat Builder, it includes.

  • 3 beautiful pages (blog, about, contact)
  • Amazing custom header.
  • New footer layout.
  • Custom page/category title with vriable icon via builder custom fields.
  • Custom single post template.
  • 2 Custom post modules template.
  • Custom product page.
  • Custom product box module template.
  • custom widget title template
  • All images is retina ready
